detaileddescription.para: Constructor for a TransporterSystem. The queueing discipline and the capacity limit of the underlying queues for the jobs and for the transporters can be chosen.

parameterdescription.para: Model : The model this TransporterSystem is associated to.
int : determines the sort order of the underlying transporter queue implementation. Choose a constant from QueueBased like QueueBased.FIFO or QueueBased.LIFO or ...
int : The capacity of the transporter queue, that is how many transporters can be enqueued. Zero (0) means unlimited capacity.

int : The capacity of the jobs queue, that is how many transporters can be enqueued. Zero (0) means unlimited capacity.

boolean : Flag for trace to produce trace messages.
